WHO   — The Spice Melange — the substance that binds the universe
WHAT  — The most precious substance in the universe, the spice melange, found only on Arrakis.
WHERE — D1 · Dune  Framework inputs: The cosmology of the Imperium  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — It binds the whole Imperium in dependence — he who controls the spice controls the universe.
HOW   — Produced in the deep desert through the life-cycle of the sandworms, it extends life, expands consciousness, and grants the limited prescience by which the Guild Navigators fold space.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  He who controls the spice controls the universe; he who can destroy a thing controls it.

